                "webTitle": "US pilot who took magic mushrooms and tried to cut engines says behavior â€˜unfathomableâ€™",
                "webUrl": "https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/article/2024/aug/23/us-pilot-magic-mushrooms-plane-engines",
                "apiUrl": "https://content.guardianapis.com/us-news/article/2024/aug/23/us-pilot-magic-mushrooms-plane-engines",
